                     <interp inst="t17850629-34-off157" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850629-34-off157" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17850629-34-cd158" type="crimeDate">24th day of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850629-34-off157 t17850629-34-cd158"></join>, one silver watch, value 40 s. and one pair of silver shoe buckles, value 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17850629-34-victim319" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
                           Cox
                        <interp inst="t17850629-34-victim319" type="surname" value="Cox"></interp>
